meet strict performance criteria this means meeting with and assessing the portfolio managers and all key personnel involved in running the funds equity funds     investing in major stock markets these funds invest in the major stock markets including london new york hong kong china and south east asia investments in global stock markets no need to manage your portfolio funds suited to your strategy only take risks you’re comfortable with diversify your portfolio for medium to longterm investing risk of loss of capital fixed income funds     regular income and access to the bond market also known as bond funds these investments offer you a regular income and a chance to diversify your portfolio designed for a consistent regular income for retirement planning excellent diversification for your portfolio strategies to suit your goals for medium to longterm investing risk of loss of capital sector funds     focusing on particular industries sector funds invest in companies that operate in a particular industry or sector our sector funds also include commodity funds invest in a single sector a range of carefully selected funds follow your individual strategy be aware of the risk of loss single sector investment is subject to higher risk unless you diversify your portfolio for medium to longterm investing risk of loss of capital money market funds     a shorterterm lowerrisk solution for shorterterm investment these lowerrisk funds can offer you higher interest rates than savings accounts although with a risk to your capital lowerrisk shortterm investments diverse portfolios to suit you highly experienced fund managers save by pooling your resources risk of loss of capital exchange traded funds     exchange traded funds etfs for flexibility our exchange traded funds etfs offer the portfolio diversification of a fund but can be traded like shares diversification for your portfolio easy flexible trading ideal for diverse small investments for medium to longterm investing risk of loss of capital contact us online contact form quick links multimanager globalbeta structured products compass q 6  at the beginning of this year many market participants saw the fall in equity prices as a precursor to the end of this economic cycle even in the absence of a recession many forecasted a further slide in equity prices as markets were seen as too expensive   date 6 views  views the products and services described on this page are provided by the following companies which are part of barclays barclays bank plc in england  wales barclays bank plc in isle of man barclays bank suisse sa in switzerland gerrard investment management limited in england  wales barclays private asset management monaco sam in monaco barclays group representative office nigeria limited in nigeria woolwich plan managers limited in england  wales for further information on these companies and barclays please read important information each barclays company reserves the right to make a final determination on whether or not you are eligible for any particular product or service contact us about us online contact form online banking press contacts careers map privacy  security privacy policy terms  conditions important information security cookies policy cookie settings follow us news feed linked in follow us on twitter products and services on this site may not be available in certain jurisdictions in particular these products and services are not being offered in japan or the united states or to us residents for full details of exclusions and disclaimers please see the important information before proceeding each barclays company reserves the right to make a final determination on whether or not you are eligible for any particular product or service this page is operated by barclays outside of the united states in accordance with us regulation the use of twitter and other social media websites for communication with barclays is prohibited if you have an account operated in the